Welcome to TOPSIM - Project Management!

  With your participants' system you can analyze the network diagram 
  of your project, enter your decisions and optimize your project. 
  Use the "Reports" menu to view your results for the current period.

  You enter your decisions in the network diagram or by choosing the 
  menu “Alternative Course of Actions”

  You receive an overview of the functions by clicking on the menu. 
  You will find explanations for the various menu functions in the 
  Help section.

  We wish you an enjoyable and successful game!
